        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>FAA and TSA Family and Medical Leave Act</b></p> <p>This bill revises the personnel management system of the Federal Aviation Administration (FAA) to provide FAA employees, including Transportation Security Administration employees, the same family and medical leave benefits as other federal employees.</p>]]></text>
